[{"id": 608411, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 434, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3661, "text": "Hamt, F\u00e2t\u0131r olan Allah'ad\u0131r; g\u00f6kleri ve yeri yaratan, melekleri iki\u015fer, \u00fc\u00e7er, d\u00f6rder kanatl\u0131 el\u00e7iler yapan O'dur. Yarat\u0131\u015fta/yarat\u0131lm\u0131\u015flarda diledi\u011fini art\u0131r\u0131r O. Hi\u00e7 ku\u015fkusuz, Allah her \u015feye g\u00fcc\u00fc yetendir."}, {"id": 608412, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 434, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3662, "text": "Allah'\u0131n insanlar i\u00e7in a\u00e7\u0131p yayd\u0131\u011f\u0131 rahmeti hi\u00e7 kimse tutup k\u0131samaz. Onun tutup k\u0131st\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131 ise O'ndan sonra sal\u0131p a\u00e7acak yoktur. Az\u00eez'dir O, Hak\u00eem'dir."}, {"id": 608413, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 434, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3663, "text": "Ey insanlar, Allah'\u0131n, \u00fczerinizdeki nimetini an\u0131n! Allah'tan ba\u015fka yarat\u0131c\u0131 m\u0131 var? Sizi g\u00f6kten ve yerden r\u0131z\u0131kland\u0131r\u0131r. O'ndan ba\u015fka ilah yoktur. Hal b\u00f6yle iken nas\u0131l oluyor da y\u00fcz geri \u00e7evriliyorsunuz?"}, {"id": 608414, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3664, "text": "E\u011fer seni yalanl\u0131yorlarsa, senden \u00f6nceki resuller de yalanlanm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r. B\u00fct\u00fcn i\u015fler ve olu\u015flar Allah'a d\u00f6nd\u00fcr\u00fcl\u00fcr."}, {"id": 608415, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3665, "text": "Ey insanlar, Allah'\u0131n vaadi hakt\u0131r! O halde i\u011freti d\u00fcnya hayat\u0131 sizi sak\u0131n aldatmas\u0131n! O yaman aldat\u0131c\u0131, o \u00e7ok gururlu, sizi sak\u0131n Allah ile aldatmas\u0131n."}, {"id": 608416, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3666, "text": "\u015eu bir ger\u00e7ek ki, \u015feytan sizin i\u00e7in bir d\u00fc\u015fmand\u0131r. O halde siz de onu d\u00fc\u015fman tutun. Hi\u00e7 ku\u015fkusuz, o kendi hizbini cehennem y\u00e2ran\u0131ndan olmalar\u0131 i\u00e7in \u00e7a\u011f\u0131r\u0131r durur."}, {"id": 608417, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 376, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3667, "text": "K\u00fcfre sapanlar i\u00e7in \u015fiddetli bir azap vard\u0131r. \u0130man edip hayra ve bar\u0131\u015fa y\u00f6nelik ameller i\u015fleyenlere gelince onlar i\u00e7in bir ba\u011f\u0131\u015flanma ve b\u00fcy\u00fck bir \u00f6d\u00fcl olacakt\u0131r."}, {"id": 608418, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3668, "text": "Ya o ki\u015fi? Yapt\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131n k\u00f6t\u00fcl\u00fc\u011f\u00fc kendisine allan\u0131p pullanm\u0131\u015f da onu g\u00fczel g\u00f6r\u00fcvermi\u015f. Do\u011frusu \u015fu: Allah diledi\u011fini/dileyeni sapt\u0131r\u0131r, diledi\u011fini/dileyeni de do\u011fruya ve g\u00fczele k\u0131lavuzlar. O halde can\u0131n onlar i\u00e7in \u00fcz\u00fcnt\u00fclere dalmas\u0131n. Hi\u00e7 ku\u015fkusuz, Allah onlar\u0131n \u00fcrettiklerini/ortaya koyduklar\u0131 oyunlar\u0131 \u00e7ok iyi bilmektedir."}, {"id": 608419, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3669, "text": "Allah odur ki, r\u00fczg\u00e2rlar\u0131 g\u00f6nderdi. R\u00fczg\u00e2rlar bir bulut kald\u0131r\u0131r. Derken onu \u00f6l\u00fc bir beldeye sevk ettik de \u00f6l\u00fcm\u00fcnden sonra topra\u011fa onunla hayat verdik. \u0130\u015fte \u00f6l\u00fcm\u00fcnden sonra dirilme de b\u00f6yledir."}, {"id": 608420, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3670, "text": "Onur ve y\u00fccelik isteyen bilsin ki, onur ve y\u00fcceli\u011fin t\u00fcm\u00fc Allah'ad\u0131r. Temiz ve g\u00fczel kelime O'na y\u00fckselir; hayra ve bar\u0131\u015fa y\u00f6nelik amel de o kelimeyi y\u00fcceltir. K\u00f6t\u00fcl\u00fckleri kuranlara/k\u00f6t\u00fcl\u00fckleri tuzak yapanlara gelince, onlar i\u00e7in \u015fiddetli bir azap vard\u0131r. Ve b\u00f6ylelerinin tuza\u011f\u0131 tarumar olur."}, {"id": 608421, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 435, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3671, "text": "Allah sizi bir topraktan, sonra bir spermden yaratt\u0131; sonra sizi \u00e7iftler haline getirdi. O'nun ilmi d\u0131\u015f\u0131nda, bir di\u015fi ne hamile olur ne de do\u011furur. Ya\u015fayan bir varl\u0131\u011fa daha \u00e7ok \u00f6m\u00fcr verilmesi de onun \u00f6mr\u00fcnden biraz azalt\u0131lmas\u0131 da mutlaka bir kitapta yaz\u0131l\u0131d\u0131r. Bu, Allah i\u00e7in ger\u00e7ekten \u00e7ok kolayd\u0131r."}, {"id": 608422, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3672, "text": "\u0130ki deniz birbirine e\u015fit olmaz. Bu tatl\u0131d\u0131r, susuzlu\u011fu giderir, i\u00e7imi ho\u015f ve rahatt\u0131r; \u015fu tuzludur, ac\u0131d\u0131r. Ama hepsinden de taze et yersiniz; giyip tak\u0131naca\u011f\u0131n\u0131z bir s\u00fcs \u00e7\u0131kar\u0131rs\u0131n\u0131z. Allah'\u0131n l\u00fctfundan nasip araman\u0131z ve \u015f\u00fckredebilmeniz i\u00e7in, gemilerin denizi yara yara gitti\u011fini g\u00f6r\u00fcrs\u00fcn."}, {"id": 608423, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3673, "text": "Allah, geceyi g\u00fcnd\u00fcz\u00fcn i\u00e7ine sokar, g\u00fcnd\u00fcz\u00fc de gecenin i\u00e7ine sokar. G\u00fcne\u015f'i ve Ay'\u0131 buyruk alt\u0131na alm\u0131\u015ft\u0131r. Her biri belirlenen bir s\u00fcreye kadar ak\u0131p gidiyor. \u0130\u015fte Rabbiniz Allah bu; m\u00fclk ve y\u00f6netim O'nundur. Onun berisinden yakard\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131z ise bir \u00e7ekirdek zar\u0131na bile h\u00fckmedemezler."}, {"id": 608424, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 377, "hizb_quarter": 174, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3674, "text": "Onlara \u00e7a\u011f\u0131rsan\u0131z, \u00e7a\u011fr\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 duymazlar. Duysalar da size cevap veremezler. K\u0131yamet g\u00fcn\u00fc de sizin onlar\u0131 ortak ko\u015ftu\u011funuzu ink\u00e2r ederler. Hi\u00e7 kimse sana, Hab\u00eer olan Allah'\u0131n verdi\u011fi gibi haber veremez."}, {"id": 608425, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3675, "text": "Ey insanlar, siz Allah'a y\u00f6nelmi\u015f yoksullars\u0131n\u0131z! Allah ise mutlak Gan\u00ee, mutlak Ham\u00eed'dir."}, {"id": 608426, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3676, "text": "Dilerse sizi yok eder, yepyeni bir halk getirir."}, {"id": 608427, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3677, "text": "Ve bu, Allah'a hi\u00e7 de g\u00fc\u00e7 gelmez."}, {"id": 608428, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 436, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3678, "text": "Hi\u00e7bir g\u00fcnahk\u00e2r, bir ba\u015fkas\u0131n\u0131n g\u00fcnah\u0131n\u0131 y\u00fcklenmez. Y\u00fck\u00fc a\u011f\u0131r gelen, onu ta\u015f\u0131maya \u00e7a\u011f\u0131rsa bile, kendisinden hi\u00e7bir \u015fey y\u00fcklenilmez. Akraba bile olsa... Sen ancak Rablerinden i\u00e7in i\u00e7in korkanlar\u0131 ve namaz\u0131/duay\u0131 yerine getirenleri uyar\u0131rs\u0131n. Ar\u0131n\u0131p temizlenen, kendi benli\u011fi i\u00e7in ar\u0131n\u0131p temizlenir. D\u00f6n\u00fc\u015f Allah'ad\u0131r."}, {"id": 608429, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3679, "text": "K\u00f6rle, g\u00f6ren bir olmaz!"}, {"id": 608430, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3680, "text": "Karanl\u0131klarla \u0131\u015f\u0131k da bir olmaz!"}, {"id": 608431, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3681, "text": "G\u00f6lge ile s\u0131cakl\u0131k da ayn\u0131 de\u011fildir."}, {"id": 608432, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3682, "text": "Diriler de e\u015fit olmaz, \u00f6l\u00fcler de. Allah diledi\u011fine/dileyene i\u015fittirir. Ama sen, kabirlerdekilere i\u015fittiremezsin!"}, {"id": 608433, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3683, "text": "Sen sadece bir uyar\u0131c\u0131s\u0131n!"}, {"id": 608434, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3684, "text": "\u015eu bir ger\u00e7ek ki, biz seni hak ile bir m\u00fcjdeci ve uyar\u0131c\u0131 olarak g\u00f6nderdik. Hi\u00e7bir \u00fcmmet yoktur ki, i\u00e7inden bir uyar\u0131c\u0131 gelip ge\u00e7memi\u015f olsun."}, {"id": 608435, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3685, "text": "Seni yalanl\u0131yorlarsa, onlardan \u00f6ncekiler de yalanlam\u0131\u015ft\u0131. Resulleri onlara a\u00e7\u0131k-se\u00e7ik mesajlar, sayfalar ve ayd\u0131nlat\u0131c\u0131 kitap getirmi\u015flerdi."}, {"id": 608436, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 378, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3686, "text": "Sonra ben, ink\u00e2r edenleri yakalad\u0131m. Ama nas\u0131l oldu benim azab\u0131m?!"}, {"id": 608438, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3687, "text": "G\u00f6rmedin mi, Allah, g\u00f6kten bir su indirdi. Onunla, renkleri \u00e7e\u015fit \u00e7e\u015fit meyvelar \u00e7\u0131kard\u0131k. Da\u011flardan da yollar var; beyaz, k\u0131rm\u0131z\u0131, de\u011fi\u015fik renklerde. Ve simsiyah yollar da var."}, {"id": 608440, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3688, "text": "Ayn\u0131 \u015fekilde, insanlardan, hayvanlardan, davarlardan da \u00e7e\u015fitli renklerde olanlar var. Kullar\u0131 i\u00e7inde Allah'tan ancak bilginler \u00fcrperir. Allah Az\u00eez'dir, Gaf\u00fbr'dur."}, {"id": 608441, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3689, "text": "Allah'\u0131n kitab\u0131n\u0131 okuyanlar, namaz\u0131/duay\u0131 yerine getirenler, kendilerine verdi\u011fimiz r\u0131z\u0131klardan gizli ve a\u00e7\u0131k infak edenler, asla batmayacak bir ticaret umabilirler."}, {"id": 608442, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 437, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3690, "text": "\u00c7\u00fcnk\u00fc Allah onlara \u00fccretlerini tam \u00f6deyecek, l\u00fctfundan onlara art\u0131rma da yapacakt\u0131r. Gaf\u00fbr'dur O, \u00e7ok affeder; \u015eek\u00fbr'dur, \u015f\u00fckredenlere mutlaka kar\u015f\u0131l\u0131k verir."}, {"id": 608443, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3691, "text": "Kitap'tan sana vahyetti\u011fimiz, kendinden \u00f6ncekini tasdikleyici hakk\u0131n ta kendisidir. Allah, kullar\u0131ndan tam haberdard\u0131r, onlar\u0131 iyice g\u00f6rmektedir."}, {"id": 608444, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3692, "text": "Sonra, kullar\u0131m\u0131z aras\u0131ndan se\u00e7tiklerimizi kitaba miras\u00e7\u0131 k\u0131ld\u0131k. \u0130\u00e7lerinden \u00f6z nefsine zulmeden var. Orta yolda gideni var. Allah'\u0131n izniyle hay\u0131rlarda \u00f6ne ge\u00e7eni var. \u0130\u015fte bu, b\u00fcy\u00fck l\u00fctfun ta kendisidir."}, {"id": 608445, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3693, "text": "Adn cennetlerine girerler onlar, orada alt\u0131ndan bilezikler ve inci tak\u0131n\u0131rlar. Orada giysileri ise ipektir."}, {"id": 608446, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3694, "text": "\u015e\u00f6yle derler: \"Hamt olsun, \u00fcz\u00fcnt\u00fcy\u00fc bizden gideren Allah'a! Rabbimiz mutlak Gaf\u00fbr, mutlak \u015eek\u00fbr'dur."}, {"id": 608447, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3695, "text": "L\u00fctfuyla bizi durulacak yurda kondurdu. Orada bize hi\u00e7bir yorgunluk dokunmaz. Orada bize hi\u00e7bir usan\u00e7 da dokunmaz.\""}, {"id": 608448, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3696, "text": "\u0130nk\u00e2r edenlere de cehennem ate\u015fi var. Ne haklar\u0131nda h\u00fck\u00fcm verilir ki \u00f6ls\u00fcnler ne de azaplar\u0131 hafifletilir. \u0130\u015fte b\u00f6yle cezaland\u0131r\u0131r\u0131z t\u00fcm nank\u00f6rleri biz."}, {"id": 608449, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 379, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3697, "text": "Feryat edip dururlar orada: \"Rabbimiz, \u00e7\u0131kar bizi de \u00f6nceden yapt\u0131\u011f\u0131m\u0131zdan ba\u015fka \u015fey yapal\u0131m. Bar\u0131\u015fa ve hayra y\u00f6nelik iyi bir i\u015f yapal\u0131m.\" Sizi biz, \u00f6\u011f\u00fct alan\u0131n \u00f6\u011f\u00fct alaca\u011f\u0131 bir s\u00fcre \u00f6m\u00fcrlendirmedik mi? Uyar\u0131c\u0131 da geldi size. Hadi, tad\u0131n bakal\u0131m azab\u0131! Zalimler i\u00e7in hi\u00e7bir yard\u0131mc\u0131 yok art\u0131k."}, {"id": 608450, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 438, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3698, "text": "Allah, g\u00f6klerin ve yerin gayb\u0131n\u0131 bilendir/\u00c2lim'dir. O, g\u00f6\u011f\u00fcslerin \u00f6z\u00fcndekini de \u00e7ok iyi bilir."}, {"id": 608451, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 439, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3699, "text": "Sizi yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde halefler yapan O'dur. Nank\u00f6rl\u00fck edenin nank\u00f6rl\u00fc\u011f\u00fc kendi aleyhinedir. K\u00e2firlerin k\u00fcfr\u00fc, Rableri kat\u0131nda \u00f6fkeden ba\u015fka bir \u015fey art\u0131rmaz. K\u00e2firlerin k\u00fcfr\u00fc h\u00fcsran ve y\u0131k\u0131mdan ba\u015fka bir \u015fey art\u0131rmaz."}, {"id": 608452, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 439, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 175, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3700, "text": "De ki: \"Allah'\u0131n berisinden yakard\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131z \u015fu ortaklar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 g\u00f6rd\u00fcn\u00fcz m\u00fc? G\u00f6sterin bana topaktan neyi yaratt\u0131 onlar!\" Yoksa g\u00f6klerde bir ortakl\u0131klar\u0131 m\u0131 var? Yoksa onlara bir kitap verdik de kendileri o kitaptan bir kan\u0131t \u00fczerinde midirler? Hay\u0131r, zalimler birbirlerine aldan\u0131\u015ftan/aldat\u0131\u015ftan ba\u015fka hi\u00e7bir \u015fey vaat etmezler."}, {"id": 608453, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 439, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 176, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3701, "text": "Allah, g\u00f6kleri ve yeri, yok olup gitmesinler diye tutuyor. Yemin olsun, e\u011fer \u00e7\u00f6k\u00fcp giderlerse, O'ndan ba\u015fka hi\u00e7 kimse onlar\u0131 tutamaz. Hal\u00eem'dir O, Gaf\u00fbr'dur."}, {"id": 608454, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 439, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 176, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3702, "text": "Yeminlerinin t\u00fcm g\u00fcc\u00fcyle Allah'a ant i\u00e7mi\u015flerdi ki, e\u011fer kendilerine bir uyar\u0131c\u0131 gelirse, \u00fcmmetlerin herhangi birinden \u00e7ok daha do\u011fru bir gidi\u015f \u00fczere olacaklar. Fakat uyar\u0131c\u0131 onlara gelince, bu onlara nefretle ka\u00e7\u0131\u015ftan ba\u015fka bir katk\u0131 sa\u011flamad\u0131."}, {"id": 608455, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 439, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 176, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3703, "text": "Yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde kibirlendi ve k\u00f6t\u00fcl\u00fck tezg\u00e2hlad\u0131lar. Oysaki tezg\u00e2hlanan k\u00f6t\u00fcl\u00fck, sahibinden ba\u015fkas\u0131n\u0131 ku\u015fatmaz. \u00d6ncekilerin ba\u015f\u0131na gelenlerden ba\u015fkas\u0131n\u0131 m\u0131 bekliyorlar? Allah'\u0131n yol ve y\u00f6nteminde de\u011fi\u015fme asla bulamazs\u0131n! Allah'\u0131n yol ve y\u00f6nteminde d\u00f6neklik de bulamazs\u0131n!"}, {"id": 608456, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 439, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 176, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3704, "text": "Yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde dola\u015f\u0131p da kendilerinden \u00f6ncekilerin sonlar\u0131n\u0131n nas\u0131l oldu\u011funu g\u00f6rmediler mi? Onlar, kuvvet bak\u0131m\u0131ndan bunlardan daha zorluydular. G\u00f6klerde de yerde de Allah'\u0131 \u00e2ciz b\u0131rakacak hi\u00e7bir \u015fey yoktur. Al\u00eem'dir O, Kad\u00eer'dir."}, {"id": 608457, "identifier": "tr.ozturk", "surah_number": 35, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0641\u0627\u0637\u0631", "surah_en_name": "Faatir", "surah_en_name_translation": "The Originator", "revelation_type": "Meccan", "juz": 22, "manzil": 5, "page": 440, "ruku": 380, "hizb_quarter": 176, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "\u00d6zt\u00fcrk", "transelator_en_name": "Yasar Nuri Ozturk", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 3705, "text": "E\u011fer Allah, insanlar\u0131, kazand\u0131klar\u0131 y\u00fcz\u00fcnden hesaba \u00e7ekseydi, yerk\u00fcrenin s\u0131rt\u0131nda hi\u00e7bir canl\u0131 b\u0131rakmazd\u0131. Ne var ki, onlar\u0131 belirli bir s\u00fcreye kadar, ecelleri gelinceye kadar erteliyor. Allah, kullar\u0131n\u0131 iyice g\u00f6rmektedir."}]